WEBVTT

00:01:00.800 --> 00:01:04.319
Your phone is not very natural.

00:01:05.099 --> 00:01:07.576
And you probably think
you're addicted to your phone,

00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:08.840
but you're really not.

00:01:09.240 --> 00:01:11.280
We're not addicted to devices,

00:01:11.320 --> 00:01:14.400
we're addicted to the information
that flows through them.

00:01:14.680 --> 00:01:17.640
I wonder how long you would be
happy in your happy place

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:20.800
without any information
from the outside world.

00:01:21.520 --> 00:01:23.806
I'm interested in how we access
that information,

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:25.840
how we experience it.

00:01:25.880 --> 00:01:29.880
We're moving from a time
of static information,

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:32.880
held in books and libraries and bus stops,